## 2. `loop.config.yml`\
\
```yaml\
project:\
  name: "any-project"\
  test_command: "<how this project runs tests>"   # e.g. pytest -q / npm test / go test ./...\
  lint_command: "<how this project lints>"         # e.g. ruff check . / eslint . / golangci-lint run\
  build_command: "<how this project builds>"       # e.g. npm run build / cargo build\
\
files:\
  vision_file: "VISION.md"\
  state_file: "LOOP_STATE.md"\
\
parallelism: 3   # set to how many PRs you can genuinely REVIEW per day, not the max the tool can spawn\
```\
\
