## 4. `VISION.md` (upgraded template)\
\
```markdown\
<!-- Style: guardrail | minimal | product | narrative  (bootstrap picks; you confirm) -->\
# Vision: <Project Name>\
\
## Core Problem\
<One sentence: the problem and why it matters.>\
\
## Intended Solution\
<High-level approach. No implementation details.>\
\
## Target Users & Use Cases\
<Who it's for; the primary flows.>\
\
## Current Priorities (in order)\
1. <highest-leverage goal>\
2. <next>\
3. <next>\
\
## Non-Goals (do NOT spend effort here)   <!-- highest-leverage section for drift prevention -->\
- <out of scope / won't touch>\
- <thing that's out of scope for now>\
\
## Core Principles & Constraints\
<Tech philosophy, performance/security constraints, naming & style conventions.>\
\
## High-Level Architecture\
<Major components. Agents may propose updates; you approve.>\
\
## Definition of "good"\
<What "done" really means; the quality bar.>\
```\
\
(Churning status / next-epics deliberately live in `LOOP_STATE.md`, not here.)\
