## 5. `LOOP_STATE.md`\
\
```markdown\
# Loop State\
\
## Open (needs work)\
<!-- [finding] -> serves priority #N -->\
\
## In Progress\
<!-- [finding]  explorer:done fixer:running reviewer:pending  worktree: wt-xxx-01 -->\
\
## Done (this week)\
\
## Needs human review\
<!-- conflicts, non-goal work, anything the loop couldn't safely handle -->\
```\
